<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />Surely my eyes are on you, Yahweh, Lord;</para>

<para style="q1">in you I take refuge; do not leave my soul defenseless.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />Protect me from the snares that they have laid for me,</para>

<para style="q1">from the traps of evildoers.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />Let the wicked fall into their own nets</para>

<para style="q1">while I escape.</para>
